M|📊 O|tx|---
M|Acti|tx|1. **Scale acquisition aggressively** — Unit economics are strong (see `saas-economics-efficiency-metrics` for CAC/LTV)
M|Acti|tx|2. **Improve onboarding** — Reduce early churn from 5% to 3% in first 90 days
M|Acti|tx|3. **Expand cross-sell** — Push integrations add-on to 30% of base w/o it (potential +$30K MRR)
M|Acti|tx|4. **tst premium tier** — 20 enterprise cs show willingness to pay 2x for advanced features
M|Acti|tx|5. **Monitor cohort retention** — Continue tracking that new cohorts retain better than old
